1298
01:35:58,086 --> 01:36:00,053
Because I love you.

1299
01:36:00,055 --> 01:36:01,921
<i>Doctor.</i>

1300
01:36:01,923 --> 01:36:04,457
<i>Doctor Henry Frankenstein.</i>

1301
01:36:04,459 --> 01:36:09,129
<i>Henry, not Victor just
