Come out, come out.

1335
01:40:49,944 --> 01:40:52,945
Oh, there you are.

1336
01:40:52,947 --> 01:40:56,682
You do look perturbed, Henry.

1337
01:40:56,684 --> 01:40:59,652
Whatever made you
kill your girl?

1338
01:40:59,654 --> 01:41:01,954
I mean, you know, look, I'm not

